    "template": "content",
    "texts": [
     "{\"template\":\"intro\",\"texts\":[\"If your vehicle is involved in a contravention on the red route, you'll be sent a Penalty Charge Notice (PCN) for £130. You need to pay this within 28 days.\"],\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "If you pay this within 14 or 21 days (it will say on the PCN), the amount will be reduced to £65.",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"What you need\"}",
     "{\"template\":\"bulletlist\",\"items\":[\"PCN number\",\"Number plate (Vehicle Registration Mark)\",\"Credit or debit card details\"]}",
     "If instead of paying you want to dispute the charge, find out how to make a representation to \u003ca href=\"/modes/driving/red-routes/penalty-charge-notices/make-a-representation\"\u003echallenge the PCN\u003c/a\u003e .",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Pay online\"}",
     "{\"template\":\"start-row\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"end-row\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Pay by phone\"}",
     "\u003cstrong\u003ePhone: \u003c/strong\u003e 0343 222 3333 ( \u003ca href=\"/corporate/terms-and-conditions/tfl-call-charges\"\u003eTfL call charges\u003c/a\u003e )\u003cbr /\u003eLines are open 08:00-20:00 Monday to Friday, closed weekends and bank holidays.",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Pay by post\"}",
     "Red routes\u003cbr /\u003ePO Box 335\u003cbr /\u003eDarlington DL1 9PU",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Paying late\"}",
     "You get a 50% discount if you pay within 14 or 21 days (it will say on the PCN).",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Other PCNs\"}",
     "If your PCN has been issued by a Local Authority, please \u003ca href=\"/modes/driving/red-routes/penalty-charge-notices/local-authority-pcns\"\u003econtact them directly\u003c/a\u003e ."
    ],
